Ahmet and Jerry are
flying in tonight,

393
00:16:45,923 --> 00:16:49,468
so will you put them off
until I can talk
things out with ABC?

394
00:16:51,595 --> 00:16:54,056
Well, my mama said,
ain't nothing wrong
with talking.

395
00:16:55,182 --> 00:16:56,225
Hey, enough of
the formalities.

396
00:16:56,308 --> 00:16:58,227
Come on, let's go back
into the office, Ray.

397
00:16:58,310 --> 00:16:59,353
I hope I can call you Ray.

398
00:16:59,394 --> 00:17:00,896
I want you to be
comfortable here.

399
00:17:00,938 --> 00:17:04,024
Because I'll tell you
something, everything is
gonna be better at ABC.

400
