you know, I've been
at Atlantic for so long,

404
00:17:15,244 --> 00:17:19,540
I just want to give
those guys a chance, you know,
to at least match the offer.

405
00:17:19,623 --> 00:17:21,834
Mm-hmm.
Oh, certainly, certainly.

406
00:17:21,959 --> 00:17:23,418
But, uh, I doubt
they'll be able to.

