410
00:17:38,392 --> 00:17:39,434
Well,

411
00:17:39,518 --> 00:17:41,728
Ray, we've... we've never
done that before.

412
00:17:41,854 --> 00:17:43,856
No record company has.

413
00:17:43,981 --> 00:17:48,694
Well, I think I'm going to
have to have it that way for
me to leave Atlantic Records.

414
00:17:57,536 --> 00:17:59,872
Ahmet believes
we're family here at Atlantic.

415
00:17:59,955 --> 00:18:01,999
I believe we're family
here at Atlantic.

416
00:18:02,040 --> 00:18:03,876
Obviously, you don't!

417
00:18:04,334 --> 00:18:05,961
Ahmet wouldn't believe it.

418
00:18:06,003 --> 00:18:07,588
You know what he said, Ray?

419
00:18:07,671 --> 00:18:09,590
He said you would never
turn your back on us.

420
00:18:09,715 --> 00:18:11,842
Never for a schlockmeister
like Sam Clark!

421
00:18:13,010 --> 00:18:15,012
That's rich.
Sam Clark's a corporate slug,

422
00:18:15,137 --> 00:18:18,307
