the difference between
Earl Hines and Art Tatum!

423
00:18:24,605 --> 00:18:26,648
We let you grow here, Ray.

424
00:18:27,024 --> 00:18:30,652
And nobody's taking
credit for your talent,
but we nourished it.

425
00:18:31,153 --> 00:18:33,155
We let you do your thing.

426
00:18:34,740 --> 00:18:36,909
God damn it!
We deserve better than this.

427
00:18:36,950 --> 00:18:39,036
You know what,
don't think that
I don't appreciate

428
00:18:39,077 --> 00:18:40,913
everything you guys
have done here, Jerry.

429
00:18:40,996 --> 00:18:43,624
Ahmet, I'm very
proud of the work that
we've done here together.

430
00:18:43,707 --> 00:18:46,919
But, Atlantic has done
pretty good money-wise
on my records, haven't they?

431
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:48,378
Yes, we've done
very well, Ray.

432
00:18:48,504 --> 00:18:51,673
You... you were the ones that
taught me that making a record
is business,

433
00:18:51,757 --> 00:18:54,176
and find the best
business deal you can.

434
00:18:54,218 --> 00:18:57,513
Now, 75 cents of every dollar,
and owning my own masters

